<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Réinitialisation du mot de passe</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Ajout de la police Poppins -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0f7f1, #ffffff);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .message-container {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0px 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            height: auto;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .message-container h2 {
            color: #5D7052;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .message-container p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .message-container a {
            color: #5D7052;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .message-container a:hover {
            color: #4C5B3A;
        }

        .alert {
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            color: #721c24;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            animation: fadeInError 0.5s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes fadeInError {
            0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
            100% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .message-container .btn-custom {
            background: #5D7052;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            width: 100%;
            border: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: 0.3s ease-in-out;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .message-container .btn-custom:hover {
            background: #4C5B3A;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .message-container .btn-custom:active {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="message-container">
        <h2>Réinitialisation du mot de passe</h2>

        <p>
            Si un compte correspondant à votre email existe, un email vient de vous être envoyé contenant un lien pour réinitialiser votre mot de passe.
            Ce lien expirera dans {{ resetToken.expirationMessageKey|trans(resetToken.expirationMessageData, 'ResetPasswordBundle') }}.
        </p>
        
        <p>
            Si vous ne recevez pas cet email, veuillez vérifier votre dossier spam ou <a href="{{ path('app_forgot_password_request') }}">réessayer</a>.
        </p>

        <a href="{{ path('app_forgot_password_request') }}">
            <button class="btn btn-custom">Réessayer</button>
        </a>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
